name: Femboy Hooters
description: Creates femboys wearing orange, white, and close enough text on their shirt. Made with ~50 images. Works best at high weights and while it can do somewhat photorealistic, the dataset was primarily anime images. Better results come when using short shorts, croptop, and feminine or otoko no ko (I prefer feminine, but results may vary depending on your model). You can also use restaurant which seems to give better results. bulge will create large lumps in their pants, you may want to use it at a lower weight. All preview images were generated with grapefruitV4
